title: Week 6 NFL DFS Picks & Advice (Fantasy Football 10/15)
description:
It's another far-from-normal week in the NFL but at this point, Sunday seems pretty standard for DFS purposes. Will Brinson is joined by Heath Cummings and Frank Stampfl like he is every Thursday to break down the slate of games. 
Falcons-Vikings (4:55)
Lions-Jags (11:25)
Packers-Bucs (14:15)
Browns-Steelers (18:50)
Jets-Dolphins (23:15)
Texans-Titans (27:30)
Ravens-Eagles (34:45)
Bengals-Colts (38:15)
Broncos-Patriots (40:45)
Bears-Panthers (43:00)
Washington-Giants (44:00)
Rams-49ers (45:00) 
Can't forget beer talk to close us out!
